article_id:3009,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Remix Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia Remix started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1657864800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Adventurers and dragons added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers and dragons may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured adventurers returning for a limited time:</div><div>5★ Yukimura (shadow/lance)</div><div>5★ Nobunaga (flame/blade)</div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured dragon returning for a limited time:</div><div>5★ Gozu Tenno (flame)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">In addition to the above, certain limited-time adventurers and dragons from past summon showcases make their return but are not featured.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.80% (Adventurers: 1.00%, Dragons: 0.80%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 4.20% (Adventurers: 2.00%, Dragons: 2.20%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1657864800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1658210399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the returning limited-time featured adventurers and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Adventurers:</div><div>
