			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies and<br>activates "Skill Shift" if the attack connects.<br>Phase II increases the skill's area of effect,<br>while Phase III increases its area of effect even<br>more and unleashes the user's fighting spirit.<br>The user will be immune to knockback during<br>this attack.<br><br>If this skill is used after the user's fighting<br>spirit has been unleashed, a variant called<br>Monkey-Tiger Wrath will be used instead.<br>Monkey-Tiger Wrath deals damage to enemies<br>directly ahead and applies a burst gambit<br>called "Monkey's Burst." Tapping the screen a set<br>number of times during the attack will power up<br>its final hit, which will deal increased damage,<br>apply Monkey's Burst again, and partially fill the<br>skill gauge for Monkey-Tiger Chaos.<br><br>When Monkey's Burst is activated,<br>it will deal damage to the affected target<br>and nearby enemies.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 1,348 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,800<br><br><color=#00008B>Phase II:</color><br>Damage: 1,722 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,800<br><br><color=#00008B>Phase III:</color><br>Damage: 987 × 2 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 7,800<br><br><color=#00008B>When Fighting Spirit Is Unleashed:</color><br>Damage: 375 × 4 hits<br>Damage: 584 × 1 hit (MAX)<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,980<br>Special Effects:<br>・Monkey's Burst<br>　　Burst Gambit Counter: 15<br>　　Damage: 4,300 × 1 hit<br>・Skill Prep<br>　　Potency: 15%</div></dd><dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
